title: Just Watched SPIDER-MAN NO WAY HOME! Instant Reaction & Honest Thoughts Review!
author: The Reel Rejects
description:
RIGHT OUT OF THEATER REVIEW (NO SPOILERS) For Spider-Man No Way Home! The Marvel Phase 4 Film starring Tom Holland (Peter Parker), Green Goblin (Willem Dafoe), Doc Ock (Doctor Octopus Alfred Molina), Electro (Jamie Foxx), Zendaya, Jacob Batalon, Sandman, & The Lizard. Does it live up to the hype?! Does it also feature Tobey Maguire & Andrew Garfield? We won't tell you if it does or doesn't lol.
